'''義大利醬'''（Italian dressing）是一種美式沙拉醬，通常以水、醋、檸檬汁、植物油、碎青椒、糖、玉米糖漿、與各種香料製成。

但是在義大利並不使用義大利醬，義大利人吃沙拉時通常是直接使用餐桌上的橄欖油、醋、檸檬汁、鹽、香醋調味，而非預先調製好醬料。<ref>{{cite book   | title = Biba's Northern Italian Cooking | author= Biba Caggiano |publisher = Penguin | location=   |url = https://books.google.com/books?id=zdkNv16vJd4C&pg=PA188&dq=salad+dressing+in+Italy#v=onepage | date = 2002  | page =  188 | isbn = 9781440623912 | accessdate = 4 February 2016 }}</ref>義大利醬通常也用作醃製肉、蔬菜、油炸食物與作為三明治的醬汁。<ref>{{cite book   | title = The Culinary Herpetologist | author= Ernest A. Liner |publisher = Bibliomania | location=   |url = https://books.google.com/books?id=KuPdm0uvwV4C&pg=PA147&dq=italian+dressing+marinade#v=onepage | date = 2005  | page =  147 | isbn = 9781932871067 | accessdate = 4 February 2016 }}</ref>

